REVERT

GO

If "IsClustered" returns "1", "IsHadrEnabled" returns "0", and any permissions have been granted to the Local System account beyond "CONNECT SQL", "VIEW SERVER STATE", and "VIEW ANY DATABASE", this is a finding.
 
